Repository or Repo = Folder/ Directory/Project Folder
Commit => Save
Commit new file = save new file
commit changes = save changes
hashes = hash codes
branches
Tree => Represents the entire Repository

Branches
    |
    |______Master Branches-> all the history of commit goes in here in the direct repository
    |______Slave Branches/Sub Branches --> we can create and work on different or sub directories of the main repositories while keeping our 
            master branches clean from new branches /version of the same project /or whatever experimental.
